title: Ryouki no Ori: Dai 2 Shou (The Bizarre Cage)
synopsis: Masakazu Inouye enters a dark dungeon. The eyes of a girl fill with terror. Gogged and chained, she is unable to defend herself from the horrible assault that follows...
